parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing the Takata airbag recall can lead to a potentially life-threatening situation, as the faulty airbag inflators can cause serious injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: as the issue is related to a potential failure of the airbag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag light can indicate a potential problem with the airbag system, which can lead to a failure to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag light on the dashboard illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The lack of response from dealerships can lead to frustration and a sense of neglect, potentially causing owners to delay or forego necessary repairs, which can lead to a potentially life-threatening situation.
symptoms: Dealerships are unresponsive or unhelpful in addressing the Takata airbag recall.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking of the dashboard can cause sharp plastic shards to become airborne during airbag deployment, potentially leading to catastrophic injuries or death.
symptoms: often near the airbag or instrument cluster
which can spread over time; rattling or creaking noises from the dashboard; distraction due to the noise and visual appearance of the cracks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle position sensor can cause the engine to run rough, leading to decreased performance and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: Check engine light turning on; engine running rough; bad firing on plug 7; replacement of throttle position sensor does not resolve the issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling off of chrome plating on interior door handles can cause cuts and injuries to passengers.
symptoms: Chrome plating peeling off on interior door handles; cuts and injuries to fingers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The peeling off of interior paint on radio buttons and steering wheel can cause aesthetic issues and potentially lead to further damage.
symptoms: Interior paint peeling off on radio buttons and steering wheel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the plastic jack wing nut can cause the jack to become inaccessible, leading to safety issues during tire changes.
symptoms: Plastic jack wing nut twisting off; lug wrench twisting apart when used to loosen lug nuts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracking and failure of the dashboard can cause sharp edges and projectiles in the event of an airbag deployment, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
The failure of the interior door handles can cause sharp edges and cuts to hands and fingers, potentially leading to infections or transmission of diseases.
symptoms: cuts and injuries to hands and fingers

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine mounts can cause the engine to twist and clunk, potentially leading to engine damage or failure.
